        "career": "Professionally, the Queen of Cups indicates careers involving care—healthcare, counselling, teaching, or any work requiring emotional intelligence. This card supports leading with compassion, trusting your intuition about work, or creating emotionally safe workplaces. The Queen of Cups reminds you: your emotional intelligence is an asset. Use it.",
