        "career": "Professionally, the Ace of Pentacles is one of the strongest cards for new opportunities—job offers, business ventures, or financial prospects. This card supports taking calculated risks, investing in your skills, or starting new projects. The Ace of Pentacles reminds you: opportunity is here. Recognise it. Seize it. Build from it. Your career deserves investment. Give it.",
